headline: The Campbell's Company Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: CAMDEN, N.J-The Board of Directors of The Campbell's Company today declared a regular quarterly dividend on the company's capital stock of $0.39 per share. The quarterly dividend is payable Aug. 4,...
